    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2), a definitive example of the marque\u2019s engineering excellence. This specimen features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), producing a linear 385 hp delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Equipped with the Sport Chrono Package and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative. The exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, while the undercarriage is free of corrosion or fluid seepage. Interior ergonomics are preserved with no bolster wear or shrinkage of the leather-wrapped surfaces. Mechanically synchronized and meticulously maintained, this 997.2 represents a rare find for the purist seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
