    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and a lifetime of being stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a complete binder of service records from the same certified dealership since day one. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions perfectly. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade piece for the discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality. Single owner, non-smoker, and no accidents. You will not find a better-preserved specimen on the market.",
